name: Fur Elise Redeemer Puff Sleeve Shirt
description: 'The Redeemer' sounds like a superhero name, and rightly so. If shirts were superheroes, this luxe piece would be Wonderwoman. The Redeemer has a two-tone androgenous Western American aesthetic, with a soft dusty pink and contrasting scarlet collar. The ultimate trans-seasonal shirt, it is a timeless piece to last the years. Whilst epitomising the strength of Wonderwoman, it maintains a beautiful romantic vibe.

name: Equipment Knox Shirt True Black
description: The Knox is an oversized boyfriend shirt with the most delicious 100% washed silk fabric. Two flap pockets adorn the front, conveniently placed for holding your various personal possessions. The V-neck collar allows you to show off your precious gems and necklaces, and the unique tie-up front allows you to show off your OTHER precious gems...wink wink. Wear tucked in with a bright skirt or as a shirt dress if you're game!

name: White Suede Racedays Dress Black
description:
A White Suede signature stretch cotton dress made with bodice boning, bustier detailing, and high angular bodice sides. The bodice is structured and hugs the body like an old, dear friend. The cotton stretch allows for movement and breathing when worn, which is always a positive thing. And just when you think it's perfect already, low and behold! A rose gold exposed centre back metal zip! STOP IT!

97% COTTON 3% ELASTANE LINING: 95% POLYESTER 5% ELASTANE.

name: Desert Designs Jetson Dress DNA
description: The 'Jetson Dress' encapsulates all the dimensions of the Australian desert, exploring both the physical and spiritual planes in splashes of vibrant colour. You will be an absolute stand-out in this stunningly unique, 100% silk dress. If ever you've wanted a garment to be a talking point - this is the one for you! Shine like the desert sun lady!

name: L A I R Leather Baby Bond Choker I
description:
Black Fenix leather choker with multiple size options & mini O-ring front feature.

If there was ever a time in your life to say "Oh-Em-Gee" in a heavily-accented voice, it is when you place this leather lover on your neck. You will never feel more complete than when this is teamed with your high-necked number, or adding spunk to your girly ensemble. It's just that little bit dominatrix...or perhaps not enough. 

DISCLAIMER: We do not necessarily condone the use of bondage, but the Baby Bond Choker is a must if one is to pursue such activities.

name: L A I R Leather 50 Lashes Tote Black
description:
100% Milano leather body featuring a patent croc leather underlay, interior pocket & key loop.

The 50 lashes tote is an easy statement piece to add to any outfit, and a great size to fit all your daily necessities!

name: L A I R Leather 50 Lashes Tote White
description:
100% Milano leather body featuring a patent black leather underlay, interior pocket & key loop.

The 50 lashes tote is an easy statement piece to add to any outfit, and a great size to fit all your daily necessities!

name: Viktoria + Woods Falcon Shirt Dress
description: A denim boyfriend style shirt dress made from a thick stretch denim for a feminine silhouette. A super luxe tencel cotton, it falls superbly to create the ultimate look of casual cool. Featuring a back cut-out to spice up a dress that is alluring in its simplicity, the Falcon Shirt Dress is beautiful with boots or barefoot on a lazy Sunday morning.

name: Equipment 'Reese' Paradise Palm Print
description:
The 'Reese' is inspired by a classic men's shirt, and features a slightly oversized, boyfriend fit and single front chest pocket. The retro-cool paradise palm print triggers exotic daydreams of faraway islands, which can only be a good thing, unless you operate cranes and need to remain fully focused. 

This luxe shirt is 100% washed silk. Wear it buttoned to the top for a look that's chic and discreetly sexy.

name: Viktoria + Woods Axel Cigar Pant in Alcatraz
description: This cotton/spandex slim cut three quarter pant boasts a nickel zip detail and pocket trimmed with soft italian leather. The skinny fit is flattering yet comfortable due to the spandex, and the seam down the legs is so slimming - it's like a magical line of skinny! The understated navy and yellow-beige print would be the envy of all onlookers, either in the office or at the bar. An absolutely key piece in your wardrobe as "those" go-to pants.

name: Senso Robyn I Black Grained Kid
description:
Leather Upper, leather lining, man made sole. Heel Height 9.5cm approximately.

These stunning leather puppies can adorn your feet all through the balmy Summery days. Dress them up with an eye-catching frock or go casual with some flowy print shorts. Watch and wait for the envious eyes of all.

name: Senso Reece I - Black Grained Kid
description: Leather upper, leather lining, man made sole, with a heel height of approx 9.5cm.

name: Senso Riley III - Beige Pony
description:
Leather upper, leather lining, man made sole. Heel height 9.5cm approx.

These showstopping lace up pony heels can be worn casually with a pair of leather shorts in the warmer months or dress them up with an LBD!

name: Senso Bridgette Black Croc Printed Leather
description:
Leather upper, leather lining, man made sole, and a heel height of approximately 3cm.

How can one simple cutaway look so universally flattering on every ladies ankle? It's a mystery, and one we should not question because they look so damn good. Believe in the powers that be.

name: Viktoria + Woods Nikko T
description: A relaxed fit tee with cap sleeves. Made from a textured interlock mesh which has a translucent appearance when on. Wear with your flashiest bralette underneath to make a dazzling entrance. This tee has instant cool factor and would stun the pants off onlookers paired with skinny jeans or a leather skirt. Va-va-voom!

name: Eska Alikai Qaran Singlet
description: The holy grail of the singlet, the Qaran Singlet features leather lambskin with a croc embossed pattern. Unlike most stiff leather, it is tailored to a womanly shape, and is the perfect combo of a halter top and a low-back cami. It even thoughtfully hides the open back zip so you can feel comfortable putting the garment on your body whilst maintaining complete seamlessness. You're welcome.

name: Jamie Fame The Hand That Feeds Organic Tee
description:
Round Neck Tee
140GSM Organic Cotton
Enzyme Washed, Silk Conditioned

There's naughty innuendo in the graphic design of this simple tee, surely...is anyone else getting that? Any classic round neck B&W tee that can make someone simultaneously giggle and question the morality of their gutter-dwelling mind is a clear winner.

name: Zeka Hene Straight No Chaser White
description:
100% cotton crew neck t-shirt

The 'Straight No Chaser' graphic screen-printed on the front is almost an optical illusion, and is marked also with the Thelonius Monk graphic patch sewn on the front left chest. An additional graphic patch is sewn on the back.

This tee features a distressed print and will fade with wash and wear.

All items are hand screen-printed and finished by the designer.

Zeka Hene is an eclectic local Novocastrian brand producing some downright cool shiz. Get these wares now and you will be reveling in your own victorious foresight when Zeka Hene becomes HUGE.

name: Zeka Hene Straight No Chaser Black
description:
100% cotton crew neck t-shirt

name: Needle & Shred Get Radical Tee
description: The Get Radical Tee is a call to arms! We all need to wake up, shed our cozy cocoon of lameness and GET RADICAL! The tee is given a heavy "vintage" style enzyme wash with softeners, and is washed after print to soften inks in artwork.

name: Ksubi Ladi Ladi Muscle
description: This regular fit mens black muscle tank features the "Ladi Dadi" print in red plastisol on soft 110gsm Cotton Jersey. TheÂ€ Ksubi signature exposed side seam makes an appearance, so that your pectoral muscles can also make an appearance. The eclectic "Ladi Dadi" print is reminiscent of both pagan rituals and various undetermined iconography, but what is certain is that this print is rad.

name: Ksubi Chrome Baddies Muscle
description:
This regular fit men's black muscle tank features the iconic "Baddies" plastisol print in a chrome look printed on soft 110gsm Cotton Jersey and features the Ksubi signature exposed side seam.

Being a Baddie has never been sexier. You can't put a price on sex appeal.

name: The Less Is More Cross Tank
description: How good are tactile garments? This slate grey muscle tank is made that much cooler due to the 3-dimensional cross on the front. So simple, but it doesn't fail to pack a punch. The rolled raw edges top of the whole look to create a "I just rolled out of bed and I casually look better than you".

name: Black Noise White Rain Steak Knife Suicide Heavy Muscle
description: Do not be fooled by the misleading name - this very cool muscle tee is 100% cotton, and 0% steak. Understandably confusing. The grey on black colouring and raw hems reek of casual-cool, while the pagan symbol brings to mind mysterious nights and lucid dreaming.

name: Senso Talia III Indigo
description: Leather upper, leather lining, man made sole, approx 11cm heel height.

name: Senso Levi Black Kid/Printed Croc
description: Leather upper, leather lining, man made sole, approx 4.5cm heel height.

name: Senso Beatrix - Beige Leopard
description:
Leather upper, leather lining, man made rubber sole, 3cm heel height.

How can one simple cutaway look so universally flattering on every ladies ankle? It's a mystery, and one we should not question because they look so damn good. Believe in the powers that be.

name: Argyle Agrum White A2 Leather Top
description:
This incredible work of art needs no introduction. Nevertheless...

Optical white leather on leather (on leather on leather), it is cropped on one side and drops to the hip on the other, with incisions lending a cheeky peek. The beautifully structured top is reminiscent of modern architecture and futuristic shapes. Snap this up now before Argyle Agrum goes global, and you can claim you "totally got onto Argyle Agrum first".

name: Agrum Argyle Incision Crop Top
description: The complexity and sheer brilliance of this structured top is mind-blowing. First we have the shiveringly soft leather to tickle the senses. Secondly, we have the sexy raw hem and box fit just to throw you off the scent. And then did we mention the asymmetric squared back that drops to the waist to protect your kidneys from the cold? THIS TOP IS BASICALLY THE ULTIMATE INANIMATE OBJECT.

name: Argyle Agrum Black A2 Leather Top
description:
This incredible work of art needs no introduction. Nevertheless...

Tar black leather on leather (on leather on leather), it is cropped on one side and drops to the hip on the other, with incisions lending a cheeky peek. The beautifully structured top is reminiscent of modern architecture and futuristic shapes. Snap this up now before Argyle Agrum goes global, and you can claim you "totally got onto Argyle Agrum first".

name: Argyle Agrum White Leather Incision Skirt
description: Impeccably crafted curved hem leather skirt. Soft white leather will mould to your body, while small side cutouts will allow a breeze to whisper against your skin. The incisions down the front will ensure that you will be a standout wherever you are. Keep it monochromatic with a black leather crop top, or inject some colour into this incredible outfit. The skirt says it all, really. Maybe it would be best if you went topless.

name: Steele Beseme Pant - Adelina Tweed
description: The tailored Beseme tweed pant sits at the perfect waist height, nipping you in where you're smallest. The tapered leg boasts soft pleats into the waistband and has two pleasantly deep front scoop pockets. They end at the ankle, allowing you to expose that most provocative joint. The Beseme Pant is made from Cotton Tweed, and while that phrase brings to mind old British nanna's drinking Pimms and/or English Breakfast tea in their tweed jackets, you will conversely be looking young and hip-hop-happening. Wear it funkily with a cropped cami or to the office with a soft blouse and blazer. For the love of Tweed!

name: Viktoria + Woods Black Crusader Harem Pants
description: The Crusader harem pants are made from a thick stretchy Ponte. They feature a drop-crotch, so you can drop it like it's hot, as well as a fitted calf for a flattering shape. There is also the added benefit of secret hidden pockets, where you can hide all manner of things. They are not so secret, though, that you will leave an unwrapped hard-boiled lolly in there that collects balls of unidentified fluff over the months until it resembles a furry creature. This has happened to people. But it will not happen to you in these pants.

name: UNIF Just Blew It Muscle Tee
description:
Buttery soft 50% 50% Cotton Modal. Faded black sleeveless crew neck featuring reverse construction, small holes on body, grinding on neck and bottom hem. Each tee has been through a triple wash treatment to create just the right fade and pilling.

This is a hilarious parody of the iconic Nike "Just Do It" symbol and advertising campaign. But if you didn't get that joke immediately, you don't deserve the tee. 

Just kidding! But seriously.

name: UNIF Inhalin Muscle Tee
description:
Buttery soft 50% 50% Cotton Modal. Faded black sleeveless crew neck featuring reverse construction, small holes on body, grinding on neck and bottom hem. Each tee has been through a triple wash treatment to create just the right fade and pilling.

Someone was inhalin' the right stuff when they made this uber cool flaming tee. Amiright?!

name: Equipment Ian Femme Bright White
description:
100% silk.

You know how when you were little you spent idle afternoons imagining the day you morphed into a naturally classy and chic lady, oozing casual grace and style? Well, the Ian Femme shirt is your one way ticket to Styleville. With the rounded collar and discreet buttons, you will look and feel a million bucks, whether it's worn with jeans or tucked in with a pencil skirt.

name: Viktoria + Woods Black Hutton Shift Dress
description: The Hutton Shift Dress is a the perfect summer dress with slight racer front, high neckline detail and black binding detail along the side seams. This style sits just above the knee, because modesty is a virtue, ladies.

name: Viktoria and Woods Black and White Stripe Heist Split Tank
description:
Made in Australia from recycleable materials.

This sleeveless style has a relaxed fit shape and features an uneven hem that dips lower at the back. The stripes lend a classic Parisian feel, and looks chic with jeans or shorts, and a black hat to tip it off. So frenchy, so chic.

name: NEUW Patti Tank
description:
The Patti tank is a Neuw staple offered in washed back cotton tie dye jersey.

It boasts an oh-so casual slouchy shape and drapes softly like an old favourite. If there's any time to get psychedelic, it's right now.

Patti Tank. It's so hot right now. Patti Tank.

name: Equipment Cara Cami Natural Magic Leopard Print
description:
100% Washed Silk.

This cami feels like silky suede magic under the fingers and sits beautifully on the body. Team it with little shorties or get animalistic with a leather skirt, this cami will make you want to roar with the sheer femininity of it all. Go get em tiger.

name: Friend Of Mine Snake Shield Skirt
description:
Wrap skirt with armour shaped hem and button closure.

Snakes are deadly creatures. You too will look deadly delicious in this snake print wrap skirt. This mid-height skirt will speak volumes, so pair it with a simple cami or go sophisticated with a sheer blouse tucked in. Now you're dangerous, girl.

ON SALE!! was $199 now $149
